When the US becomes a target...and the clock is ticking...its down to one
man to save the lives of millions. The United States Military has troops
stationed in over 150 countries worldwide. For a group of rogue states,
this is unacceptable and a terrifying ultimatum is issued called
THE BLACKLIST:. A deadly countdown of terror attacks against key US
interests. With no end in sight, and no plan of action, the US government
must call on one of its most potent weapons - Sam Fisher.
